# Final-Project Data Analyst
In this repository contains a detailed explanation of the final project. 

**Project Title :-** "Strained Shelters": A view of housing cost burdens across German households over the years. 

**Objective :-** Provide affordable housing solutions for quality, sustainable and accessible homes. 

This project was collaboratively developed and completed by _**Janice Oikhala**_ and _**Himani Singh**_, whose combined efforts and contributions were essential to its success.

<br>


We are using two datasets for our analysis. <br>

First, we are working on the 'Housing Data' which showcases the Persons in main residence households: Germany, Years, household type, monthly housing cost burden for the time period of 2020 to 2024. The data is taken from [destatis.de](https://www-genesis.destatis.de/datenbank/online/statistic/12241/table/12241-0009#). <br>

The second data set shows the rental prices in the federal states of Germany for the time period of 2022 to 2024. The data can be seen at [Miet-check.de](https://www.miet-check.de/statistiken-bundeslaender.php). <br>
